:"<blockquote><blockquote>你點知自己十分良好</blockquote><br />\n冇晒幻聽妄想個D，又冇攻擊性危險行為</blockquote><br />\n可能因為你食藥先無，你問醫生停藥會否有機會穩定"},{"pid":"f74d7fe10fec8902ccab71137b028def6ea42305","tid":420632,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜野精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中左3,4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c320062106378cfa7a35f10fa80689210e45d30","tid":420632,"uid":143400,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"唔好食啦，我之前都自己停左藥，呢排精神左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9204c58f81d0f4418c47b25e60ad202d870eb9a7","tid":420632,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔係歧視樓主<br />\n不過有病就食藥啦"},{"pid":"7069e92ddf54edc4634cbdc5bcb07985ecc9814d","tid":420632,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"個醫生又大我話如果復發會對腦部做成二次傷害，我想停食但又淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99215ad4a89cddcf74939a637f6da24982a3fc6b","tid":420632,"uid":70159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"個撚個都叫樓豬停藥<br />\n好似啲人食抗生素好啲又停藥<br />\n搞到啲菌死唔哂番發又有抗藥性<br />\n搞到其他食抗生素都冇用<br />\n等陣樓豬聽撚左你地講停藥復發果陣<br />\n鬼唔望斬鳩死哂你班仆街"},{"pid":"122be8fa7a9218b8f3ddb2d541b3eb4b331f11c0","tid":420632,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好自行停葯<br />\n<br />\n否則等入院加葯<br />\n<br />\n第日仲食得多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2adf65ed6c4ed000780a9c32c7523a707668f9c","tid":420632,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"如果你真係唔駛食藥<br />\n你估醫生仲唔拿拿聲減藥停藥再叫你唔駛覆診咩<br />\n<br />\n一朝40個症要睇<br />\n你真係唔駛用藥早就叫你唔駛返嚟啦 <br />\n貪自己多嘢做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e119d88e1fc3b51a71bb9638b8e801771f08e4","tid":420632,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"自行停藥將會令香港生靈塗炭，血流成河"},{"pid":"a2fd85cb6757b798b64767c964eaabf833b6e2cd","tid":420632,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"辛苦下你繼續食啦爸打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b13c6bc17ee4f7bab2aa6ef569876450910246","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bcb55cc37b32fac4ae875da51623bd5076dec00e","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cbd20bd4f0bdda7036828533a2cc2aae756dc6c","tid":420632,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"食撚左3年，一直良好，次次要求醫生減停藥都唔撚應承<br />\n你知啦藥有3分毒，唔想為左好返既病繼續食藥，食到糖尿，肝酵素偏高(已有)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:16:03.000Z","msg":"我都想知唔覆診會唔會比人捉"},{"pid":"0c25925d07c53bd5916fd54939ef6e81f90c41c9","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"930f64eaa5e7388dba2c98fd44d4fb3d2a514efe","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d1a1d071fed611733c9c6dbd7b8f9ff550cd959","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f95be888b16d180aef58854d4946425c96819d42","tid":420632,"uid":156711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:50:33